name: I Knowledge Factory
overview:
IKF is the leading website designing and development consultant company in Pune India. We do provide other services website design in cms like Joomla, Magento, Wordpress, Drupal, web hosting and application development all under one roof.

At IKF, we do RESEARCH and IDENTIFY the TOUCH POINTS in the life of the target group. We help our clients COMMUNICATE with their customers in a strikingly RESPONSIVE way. We offer SOLUTIONS right from CONVENTIONAL brand communication tools (press ads, collaterals, outdoor, electronic media, etc) to diverse INNOVATIVE modes of communication like SEO, Web Hosting, Networking, Social Media, Viral Media and BTL activities.
